          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "15971",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Explain the reasons for common rules, including no walking on ski trails, one-way ski direction, no pets, and no skiing on snowmobile trails."
