          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Types of Cross Country Skis (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/oXIp-lJJH4E?si=yNMZNIMyDHQjO_uC"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "15973",
          "label": "4",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Discuss the basic principles of waxing for cross-country ski touring."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "How to Wax Cross-Country Skis (video)",
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/shorts/hFl9r0JapvI"
