            {
              "title": "How to Read a Topographic Map (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/CoVcRxza8nI"
            },
            {
              "title": "How to Use a Compass (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/0cF0ovA3FtY?si=HJAgHgcZCmPOcuC3"
            },
            {
              "title": "How to Use a Topographic Map and Compass (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/P1LL2FXK6o0?si=rb4_VuRCb-uql1gU"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "15977",
          "label": "8",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "On a gentle, packed slope, show some basic ways to control speed and direction. Include the straight run, traverse, side slip, step turn, wedge stop, and wedge turn maneuvers."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "How to Control Speed and Direction (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/kmw9LxutG_8"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "15978",
          "label": "9",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "On a cross-country trail, demonstrate effective propulsion by showing proper weight transfer form ski to ski, pole timing, rhythm, flow, and glide."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Basic Moves on Cross-Country Skis (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/ctrIUq9kCJI?si=QoPaYBG0365ZvZF1"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "15979",
          "label": "10",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Demonstrate your ability, on a 4-mile tour, to cope with an average variety of snow conditions. "
            },
            {
              "type": "element",
              "tag": "b",
              "attrs": {},
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Note:"
                }
              ]
            },
